fields.descriptive_line: Illustrated scene (page 234) from an open-air performance of As You Like It at Regent's Park in which Rosalind played by Miss Wynne-Matthison gives Phebe the secret of wooing. Page 233 features an article on the Robertson and Forbes-Robertson acting families. Published in The Tatler, No. 5, dated 31st July 1901, Harry Beard Collection
fields.physical_description: Double sided page from a magazine. Includes an illustrated scene (page 234) from an open-air performance of As You Like It at Regent's Parkand an article on the Robertson and Forbes-Robertson acting families.
fields.dimensions: Height: 34.6 cm Print size, Width: 23.7 cm Print size
